{"tid":852405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奧黑馬] 美企三季度盈利預計將強勁增長","createTime":"2018-10-07T23:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T10:46:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dccb62bbce7faa5e5a02d7bec47d429b8c119a9","tid":852405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"美企三季度盈利預計將強勁增長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001079665?full=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001079665%3Ffull%3Dy&d=VZw3MJ3HFo%2B70rSU20z6msKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f5b11306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001079665?full=y</a><br />\n<br />\n華爾街分析師們預測，第三季度美國藍籌股公司將實現新一輪強勁利潤增長，受到強勁經濟、企業稅削減和股票回購的支撐。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">FactSet的數據顯示，根據市場的共識預估，在截至9月底的三個月里每股盈利同比增長19.2%。此前2018年頭兩個季度已分別實現約25%的同比增長，如果第三季度的增長預估被證明屬實，那將是自2010年以來最強勁的連續三個季度增長。<br />\n</span><br />\n即將到來的盈利報告季展開之際，投資者正在竭力應對美國國債收益率急劇上揚，國債收益率上揚已在上周晚些時候壓低股市。<br />\n<br />\n「只要第三季度的盈利預期成真，股票就可能繼續表現良好。」道富環球投資(State Street Global Advisors)的邁克爾&bull;阿羅內(Michael Arone)表示。<br />\n<br />\n長期以來的主流趨勢是，在一個季度里，隨著時間推移，分析師們會逐漸調低自己的預估。然後，在理想情況下，企業盈利表現超過下調後的預估值。FastSet表示，今年第三季度期間預估值下降1.1%，但降幅低於5年、10年和15年平均水平。瑞信(Credit Suisse)的喬納森&bull;戈盧布(Jonathan Golub)表示：「從歷史上看，當經濟像現在這樣強勁時，公司往往會以更大幅度超越預期。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據該季度增長21%的共識預估，戈盧布計算出7個點來自減稅，2個點來自政府的刺激政策，這兩個因素在未來幾年不太可能重演。<br />\n<br />\n預計能源公司將在第三季度實現最大的盈利增長，主要得益於油價上漲。</span>"},{"pid":"85089b7f04b75efc81f52e9f99e689d63d8033bd","tid":852405,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:58:12.000Z","msg":"Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea51cfa2effdb2305e62f9bf0f15c91ece8d46ca","tid":852405,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"減企業稅好似唔關奧巴馬事 <br />\n蘋果因為減稅先一次過將成萬億外海資金搬返美帝"},{"pid":"ba095bdd5191d54ab62eeb7be9a1f340e42159aa","tid":852405,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ea51cfa2effdb2305e62f9bf0f15c91ece8d46ca","tid":852405,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"減企業稅好似唔關奧巴馬事 <br />\n蘋果因為減稅先一次過將成萬億外海資金搬返美帝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"左膠：全靠奧黑馬打好基礎，侵先有空間減稅！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f1969156a44321a5b4acccd5ec31179e020467","tid":852405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cafbd55c240f11c13974529f15bb86a5895bb8","tid":852405,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"前人種樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdb72cb471ff651735787e59248ad87e285b084","tid":852405,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:04:48.000Z","msg":"之前美國打中東話美國無錢 但之後打完中東isis之後無講過美國無錢既消息<br />\n<br />\n美國仲一直出兵 重反太平洋 仲打埋貿易戰 到底係點解呢"},{"pid":"8b2fa54bfd48fbdd66fcccf5d07e4b1d3558a554","tid":852405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8ac2e506d6decea8a2c52c438410d1f0d90095","tid":852405,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid